'''Old Nan''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. She was played by [[Margaret John]] and debuts in &quot;[[Lord Snow]].&quot; Margaret John passed away on 2 February 2011, after the completion of filming for the first season. According to the writers the character passed away between the first and second season.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.westeros.org/GoT/Episodes/Entry/The_North_Remembers/Book_Spoilers/ The North Remembers on Westeros.org (book spoilers)]&lt;/ref&gt; Old Nan is an elderly servant at [[Winterfell]], known for her storytelling.

